{{#isSelfProduct spuAdapter.saleType}}<div class="self-alert">温馨提示：顺丰海淘试运营期间，未付款订单超过30分钟将被自动取消，提交订单请尽快完成支付。</div>{{/isSelfProduct}}
<div class="content-t clearfix">

  <div class="box fl">
    <div class="tb-booth tb-pic tb-s310">
      <a href="{{input.selectedImgUrl}}">
        <img src="{{input.selectedImgUrl}}" rel="{{input.selectedImgUrl}}" class="jqzoom" alt="" style="cursor: crosshair;">
      </a>
    </div>

    <ul class="tb-thumb" id="thumblist">
      {{#setImgs skuAdapter.imgs spuAdapter.imgs}}

      {{#imgs}}
      <li class="thumb-item" >
        <div class="tb-pic tb-s40">
          <a href="#">
            <img src="{{sf.img thumbImgUrl}}" mid="{{sf.img midImgUrl}}" big="{{sf.img bigImgUrl}}">
          </a>
        </div>
      </li>
      {{/imgs}}

      {{/setImgs}}
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="product-intro fl {{background skuAdapter spuAdapter}}">
    <div id="name">
      <h1>{{spuAdapter.title}}</h1> <strong>{{spuAdapter.subtitle}}</strong>
    </div>
    <div class="summary">
      <div class="summary-tops clearfix">
        <div class="dd">
          <span>到手价：</span>
          <b><font>￥</font>{{sf.price skuAdapter.price}}</b>
          <div class="{{classify skuAdapter spuAdapter}}"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="dt">
          <!-- 参考价：<s>￥{{sf.price skuAdapter.oprice}}</s> -->
        </div>
        <div class="dl">
          {{spuAdapter.seller.name}}至中国大陆
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="summary-bottoms clearfix">

        {{#spuAdapter.shipping}}
        <dl class="clearfix">
          <dt class="fl">货 源 地：</dt>
          <dd>
            <span>
              <img class="sf-country-icon-s" src="{{spuAdapter.fromCountryImgUrl}}">{{spuAdapter.fromCountry}}
            </span>
          </dd>
        </dl>
        {{/spuAdapter.shipping}}

        <dl class="clearfix" style="padding-bottom:10px;">
          <dt class="fl">发货商家：</dt>
          <dd>
            <a href="#">
              <img class="sf-shop-icon-s" src="{{sf.img spuAdapter.supplierImgUrl}}"></a>
          </dd>
        </dl>
        <dl class="clearfix">
          <dt class="fl">国际物流：</dt>
          <dd>商家2-3天后发货，预计10-15天内到达</dd>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="choose clearfix">
      <div class="detail-attrs-select"></div>
      {{#isOpenBuy skuAdapter spuAdapter}}
      <dl class="clearfix">
        <dt class="fl">
          <span class="li_hd">购买数量：</span>
        </dt>
        <dd>
          <div class="fl num-bj clearfix">
            <a class="num_oper num_min fl" href="#">-</a>
            <input class="input_txt fl" value="{{input.amount}}" type="num" maxlength="6" size="3" can-value="input.amount">
            <a class="num_oper num_plus fl" href="#">+</a>
          </div>
          <p class="caution_tips fl" id="J_Tip" style="display:none;"></p>
          <input id="nAmount" type="hidden" value="1000">
        </dd>
      </dl>
      {{/isOpenBuy}}
    </div>

    <div class="choose-btns clearfix">
      {{#isOpenBuy skuAdapter spuAdapter}}
      <a href="#" class="btn-shop">立即购买</a>

      {{#spuAdapter.limit}}
      <span class="limit-buy">每人限购{{spuAdapter.limit}}件</span>
      {{/spuAdapter.limit}}

      {{/isOpenBuy}}

 <!--      {{#isOpenAddCar skuAdapter spuAdapter}}
      <a href="#" class="btn-append">加入购物车</a>
      {{/isOpenAddCar}} -->
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="m-service">
    <h2>顺丰海淘服务承诺</h2>
    <ul class="clearfix">
        <li>
            <span class="icon-service1"></span>
            <h3>直采海外</h3>
            <p>我们承诺所有在顺丰海淘网站在售商品均为海外电商、厂家供货的原装正品。</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <span class="icon-service2"></span>
            <h3>直邮中国</h3>
            <p>我们在美国、日本等商品原产地拥有仓库，为您商品的跨境运输提供了有效保障。</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <span class="icon-service3"></span>
            <h3>安心售后</h3>
            <p>非人为因素产生的商品破损或运输途中丢失，我们将第一时间安排客服处理。</p>
        </li>
    </ul>
</div>
<div class="m-detail">
    <h2>商品详情</h2>
    {{#spuAdapter.intro}}
        {{&spuAdapter.intro}}
    {{/spuAdapter.intro}}


    {{&spuAdapter.foreignDescription}}

</div>
<div class="m-tips">
    <div class="m-tips-b">
        <h2>顺丰海淘小贴士</h2>
        <ul>
            <li class="clearfix">
                <div class="m-tips-c1 left">
                    <span class="m-tips-icon">TIP01</span>
                </div>
                <div class="m-tips-c2">
                    <h3>顺丰海淘的商品都是正品吗？</h3>
                    <p>顺丰海淘所有的商品来自国外电商网站或厂商，下单后，顺丰海淘商品全部支持专柜验货，确保正品。</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="clearfix">
                <div class="m-tips-c1 left">
                    <span class="m-tips-icon">TIP02</span>
                </div>
                <div class="m-tips-c2">
                    <h3>订购商品大致需要经过哪些流程？</h3>
                    <p>在您提交支付后，可在  个人中心 > 我的订单  查询订单信息。<br>
                        一般订单处理流程有：  支付成功 > 海外商品直采 > 等待商户发货 > 报关登记 > 海关核查 > 国内发货。</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="clearfix">
                <div class="m-tips-c1 left">
                    <span class="m-tips-icon">TIP03</span>
                </div>
                <div class="m-tips-c2">
                    <h3>为什么要上传身份证信息？</h3>
                    <p>根据法律法规规定，海外商品需登记报关，海关需要核对收货人姓名与身份证是否匹配，如不匹配可能被扣关处理，大大延误收货周期，故请提供与收货人相同的身份信息。</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="clearfix">
                <div class="m-tips-c1 left">
                    <span class="m-tips-icon">TIP04</span>
                </div>
                <div class="m-tips-c2">
                    <h3>购买海外商品会被额外收税吗？</h3>
                    <p>顺丰海淘商品到手价已含运费和税费，用户仅需支付一次即可。</p>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
